{"_id":"0d96a501-654d-462c-826d-87565b5c9816","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 1: Spiritsight","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Spiritsight","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"fast","defense":"","Target":"Self","range":"","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"1","description":"One of your eyes extends into the spirit plane, with it you can see your surroundings within the plane but not affect them physically. If you are in the spirit plane, this instead allows you to see the corporeal plane.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"0f2dcf21-b38e-4d2e-b58c-61832a6b0fc1","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 3: Planar Shift","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Planar Shift","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"Self","range":"","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"","description":"The phase transition required to enter the spirit plane is complex, but with practice this spell can be used to send you into the spirit plane from the corporeal for as long as you maintain it.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"181024c0-6d3e-4bb6-a3be-e63104b75577","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 5: Call Spirit: Tentacle Garden","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Call Spirit: Tentacle Garden","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"intuition","Target":"Area","range":"Short","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"You call forth the maw of an unspeakably large spirit that dwells underground. The area becomes Obscured and all creatures within it are Slowed. When a creature enters the area or begins its turn there you make a Spirit check against it dealing Standard Agility damage.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"2efa8d9e-2804-4827-ace0-14390b023d88","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 5: Call Spirit: Weaver","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Call Spirit: Weaver","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"","description":"After one minute spent burning Spiritweed Incense and communing with the spirits, a Weaver spirit appears which can weave solid material from gossamer filaments it produces. You can direct it to create surfaces or walls of up to ten meters by ten meters so long as they are attached to something (they cannot float in midair), or a dome-like structure covering one area. If you choose a dome, all healing checks made in the area gain a boon.\nThe structure is sturdy, with level equal to your ranks (successfully damaging it decreases its level by 1). While maintaining the spell, each round you may spend a Medium action to direct the Weaver to restore the level by 1 (to a maximum equal to your ranks). The structure lasts for up to twenty-four hours after you stop maintaining the spell.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"34e1bdbb-3d24-491a-8421-b1419a467ccc","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 5: Call Spirit: Dreamer","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Call Spirit: Dreamer","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"intuition","Target":"","range":"Long","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"You call forth a Dreamer spirit to a point within range. Each round you make a Spirit check vs all living creatures within a Short range of it, and on a failure they take Standard Intuition damage. This damage cannot cause Wounds; instead creatures who would fall to zero Intuition fall asleep. Creatures who are not already in combat do not become aggressive due to this spell unless they successfully defend against it.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"3a483421-1422-4f54-a61b-10b502015f7f","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 3: Quell Spirits","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Quell Spirits","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"intuition","Target":"Single","range":"Short","Duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You deal Heavy Intuition damage to a spirit you can see. This cannot inflict Wounds, instead if the spirit would reach zero Intuition it flees, becomes calmed, or submits. If used out of combat, this is not necessarily an agressive action, however on a failure the spirit will become aggressive.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"5d9180e1-027c-4474-a33e-6a92c23455ae","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 5: Planar Breach","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Planar Breach","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"","Target":"","range":"Short","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"You create a breach to the spirit plane; it is visible and bidirectional (you may pass through it in either direction). It is about the size of a person, and must be placed in an empty space. You may also use this to close an existing breach by making a check against the Spirit skill of its creator.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"5fb51381-a4b8-416f-a9d0-32823a173fd2","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 1: Spirt Bloom","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Spirt Bloom","rank":"1","type":"technique","speed":"medium","defense":"strength","Target":"Area","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You cause millions of mindless microscopic spirits to bloom around an area, draining energy as they do so. This deals Light Agility damage.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"739d89f5-09fb-4c5c-9de9-8a7ca09ee41d","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 3: Call Spirit: Guide","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Call Spirit: Guide","rank":"3","type":"technique","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"","description":"After one minute spent burning Spiritweed Incense and communing with the spirits, a Guide spirit will appear to you to show you the way. While present, you use your Spirit skill for all checks related to navigation or for finding safety, food, shelter, or water. The guide takes on a different form for each person, and the same one appears each time you cast this spell.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"77e07f56-b46c-40ea-a57a-9c493d5426db","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 1: Call Spirit: Messenger","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Call Spirit: Messenger","rank":"1","type":"ability","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"","description":"You must burn Spiritweed incense for a minute, causing a Messenger spirit, appearing as a curved shell, to appear before you. By speaking a message of no more than one minute into the shell, you can cause it to relay that information to a person of your choice within ten kilometers of your location, appearing before them immediately after your message is complete.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"d739a9dc-62b0-4381-b82f-b0bf32c155cd","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 5: Call Spirit: Will-o'-the-Wisp","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Call Spirit: Will-o'-the-Wisp","rank":"5","type":"technique","speed":"slow","defense":"intuition","Target":"Single","range":"Long","Duration":"Maintained","cost":"3","description":"You call forth a Will-o'-the-wisp spirit that moves as you direct it and provides light similar to a lantern. If you simply use it as a light source, this takes no additional actions to maintain. If you target a creature with this spell, it takes a Slow action each round to maintain it. They are pacified and compelled to follow the spirit. Each round, you must make a new Spirit check against them, dealing Light Intuition damage on a success and ending the spell on a failure.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
{"_id":"ea1dada9-ac39-4777-b63a-f4e36e099f14","type":"Item","name":"Spirit 3: Call Spirit: Lodger","system":{"skill":"Spirit","name":"Call Spirit: Lodger","rank":"3","type":"ability","speed":"","defense":"","Target":"","range":"","Duration":"","cost":"","description":"You burn Spiritweed incense in a ritual taking a minute, summoning a Lodger spirit. The Lodger spirit enters a target, preventing the next instance of stat burn they would receive. Once inside, the Lodger remains until the target sleeps, preventing them from being affected by this spell again.","domain":"Obscura","costtype":"","category":"ability"}}
